title: Gina Carano Talks Disney Lawsuit, Beep Bop Boop-Gate, And Faith
description:
The Mandalorian and MMA star, Gina Carano, sat down with Babylon Bee editor-in-chief Kyle Mann to talk about Elon Musk and X helping her in her lawsuit against Disney, getting canceled over a ‘beep/bop/boop’, and God being bigger than all of the enemies we face in the world.
